preference.name: RDV_QSEARCH_REVISION_RULE_NAMES
preference.preference_description: Specifies the names of preferred revision rules for Design Context searches. This preference applies only if you use the cacheless search engine. Valid Values: Accepts a single string as a value. The string contains one or more valid revision rule names.
